{"tid":1269060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 唔好再理班on9藍屍","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:05:53.000Z","uid":229553,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf362e9be3e260f31a4570327c9436da45de48b","tid":1269060,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n我明白班藍屍係痴撚線 惹事生非<br />\n睇到唔少片 真心嬲<br />\n但我地應該要做嘅 要focus嘅 絕對唔係班藍屍<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家要記住 敵人係林鄭 係政府 係班高官</span></span><br />\n大家要focus返係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今晚嘅留守 同埋聽朝不舉 仲有一連串嘅活動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我要有咩實際行動<br />\n我出post只係為左提醒大家唔好俾藍屍騎劫/影響到我地<br />\n熱門已經唔見哂關於聽日嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化 不割蓆<br />\n不篤灰 不譴責</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續加油</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dc0b09c8082e622b667c4608c1ad5f084246d5","tid":1269060,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63b9c92a971bf361c6db9b02fb5acfa2bfdcfe7a","tid":1269060,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3c4f6b3e31e4916ec00effae7d1ab9058aad8c8","tid":1269060,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38b47a9e158bfb543764ab60228f5541a352fce7","tid":1269060,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:41:49.000Z","m